snippet.textDisplay:
I just returned from a trip to Nainital, was unaware of this song till something popped up on my Instagram regarding this, I was driving a two wheeler from Bheemtaal to neem Karoli baba when this song popped up atop a mountain road, the amount of serotonin rush this song gave me perfectly mixed with the beautiful Kumaoni valley and the scenery, the feeling can’t be described enough in words. Perfect timing to experience this song made it a 1000 times better.
Thank you Coke studio once again ❤
